<h5 class="small-heading margin-top-30">Heart disease</h5>Most of the people think that heart disease is probably not our problem, it often happens to other, but in reality the large number of deaths occurs due to the heart diseases in US. In case if its get severe then the patient will either end up by losing his/her life or at least disability. 
Heart disease has many different kinds among which the most common reason of heart disease is either the blockage of coronary arteries or sometimes these arteries becomes narrow, which eventually affect the blood vessels that circulates the blood to the heart. 
This particular disease is called coronary artery disease, it happens gradually over different time intervals and it’s possibly the biggest reason that causes heart attacks.
  
